---
import MainLayout from "@/layouts/MainLayout.astro";
import disputeHero from "@/assets/dispute1.png";
import martinaImg from "@/assets/martina-2.png";
import testimonialImg from "@/assets/H5.png";
import serviceImg from "@/assets/Hservice2.png";
---

<MainLayout title="Dispute Resolution Solicitors">
  <main class="w-full min-h-screen bg-white">

    <!-- PAGE WRAPPER -->
   <div class="w-full max-w-[1250px] mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-10 py-4 sm:py-6">

      <!-- HERO SECTION -->
      <section
        class="relative w-full max-w-[1250px]  mx-auto h-[750px] rounded-[30px] overflow-hidden flex flex-col justify-end items-start px-[24px] sm:px-[50px] pb-[70px]"
      >

        <!-- BACKGROUND IMAGE -->
        <img
          src={disputeHero.src}
          alt="Dispute Resolution Solicitors"
          class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover"
        />

        <!-- OVERLAY -->
        

        <!-- CONTENT -->
        <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col gap-[10px] w-full">

          <!-- TITLE -->
          <h1
            class="font-dm font-normal text-white
            text-[60px] sm:text-[80px]
            leading-[100%]
            tracking-[-0.04em]
            max-w-[1100px]"
          >
            Dispute Resolution Solicitors
          </h1>

          <!-- SUBTITLE -->
          <p
            class="font-crimson font-normal text-white
            text-[32px] sm:text-[40px]
            leading-[110%]
            tracking-[-0.04em]
            max-w-[1100px]"
          >
            Practical Solutions for Individuals & Businesses
          </p>

        </div>

      </section>

      <!-- INTRO TEXT SECTION -->
      <section
        class="reveal w-full max-w-[1250px]  mx-auto
        flex flex-col items-center justify-center
        px-[20px] sm:px-[50px]
        py-[40px] sm:py-[80px]
        gap-[40px]"
      >

        <!-- PARAGRAPH -->
        <div class="w-full max-w-[1100px]">

          <p
            class="font-dm font-normal text-[#6F6F6F]
            text-[21px]
            leading-[140%]
            tracking-[-0.005em]"
          >
            Legal conflicts are incredibly disruptive. For a private individual,
            a dispute can cause immense personal stress and financial worry. For
            a business, it can damage important relationships, drain resources,
            and impact your bottom line.

            <br /><br />

            Our goal is to resolve your conflict as efficiently and
            cost-effectively as possible. We provide expert dispute resolution
            services tailored to your specific situation.

            <br /><br />

            We offer "legal services with a personal touch" — meaning we
            listen, we cut through the legal jargon, and we focus on practical,
            forward-thinking strategies to protect your interests.

            <br /><br />

            Whether you are an employee facing a workplace grievance, an
            employer dealing with a contract breach, or a family navigating a
            contested estate, we are here to help you find a way forward.
          </p>

        </div>

        <!-- BUTTON -->
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center
          px-[22px] py-[14px]
          h-[48px]
          rounded-full
          bg-[#0B838E]
          shadow-[0px_4px_4px_rgba(0,0,0,0.25)]
          font-dm font-bold
          text-white
          text-[14px]
          leading-[140%]
          tracking-[-0.025em]
          transition-all duration-300
          hover:bg-[#096d75]"
        >
          Contact Us
        </a>

      </section>

      <!-- TEXT AND IMAGE SECTION -->
      <section
        class="w-full max-w-[1250px]  reveal mx-auto
        flex flex-col lg:flex-row
        items-start
        gap-[60px] lg:gap-[20px]
        py-[50px] sm:py-[80px]
        px-[20px] sm:px-0"
      >

        <!-- IMAGE -->
        <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2">

          <div
            class="relative
            w-full
            h-[385px] sm:h-[744px] lg:h-[970px]
            rounded-[30px]
            overflow-hidden"
          >

            <img
              src={martinaImg.src}
              alt="Alternative Dispute Resolution"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            />

            <!-- OVERLAY -->
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/5"></div>

          </div>

        </div>

        <!-- TEXT CONTENT -->
        <div
          class="w-full lg:w-1/2
          flex flex-col
          items-start
          pt-0 lg:pt-[20px]
          lg:pl-[60px]"
        >

          <div
            class="flex flex-col
            gap-[40px]
            max-w-[580px]"
          >

            <!-- TITLE -->
            <h2
              class="font-crimson font-normal text-black
              text-[50px] sm:text-[54px] lg:text-[60px]
              leading-[95%] lg:leading-[90%]
              tracking-[-0.03em]"
            >
              The Power of Alternative Dispute Resolution (ADR)
            </h2>

            <!-- PARAGRAPH -->
            <p
              class="font-dm font-normal text-[#6F6F6F]
              text-[21px]
              leading-[140%]
              tracking-[-0.005em]"
            >
              Going to court should usually be a last resort. For most clients
              seeking dispute resolution Ireland, we strongly advocate for
              alternative dispute resolution (ADR).

              <br /><br />

              ADR involves methods like mediation, conciliation, and
              arbitration.

              <br /><br />

              The benefits of choosing ADR include:

              <br /><br />

              <span class="text-black">
                Cost & Time Efficiency:
              </span>
              ADR is generally much faster and significantly less expensive
              than traditional court litigation.

              <br /><br />

              <span class="text-black">
                Confidentiality:
              </span>
              Court cases are public. ADR keeps your personal affairs or
              sensitive business information strictly private.

              <br /><br />

              <span class="text-black">
                Control:
              </span>
              Rather than having a judge impose a decision on you, ADR allows
              you to negotiate a settlement you are actually comfortable with.

              <br /><br />

              While we prioritize keeping you out of court, if civil litigation
              becomes unavoidable, our experienced partners will fiercely and
              professionally represent you to secure the best possible outcome.
            </p>

          </div>

        </div>

      </section>

      <!-- CTA TEXT SECTION -->
<section
  class="
    w-full
    max-w-[1200px]
    mx-auto
    border-t
    border-[#929292]
    flex
    justify-center
    py-[40px]
    sm:py-[80px]
    px-4
    sm:px-[80px]
    lg:px-[240px]
  "
>
  <div
    class="
      w-full
      max-w-[720px]
      flex
      flex-col
      items-center
      text-center
      gap-[30px]
      sm:gap-[40px]
    "
  >
    <h2
      class="
        font-crimson
        font-normal
        text-black
        leading-[90%]
        tracking-[-0.03em]
        text-[50px]
        sm:text-[54px]
        lg:text-[60px]
      "
    >
      Dispute Resolution for Individuals & Employees
    </h2>

    <p
      class="
        font-dm
        font-normal
        text-[#6F6F6F]
        text-[21px]
        leading-[140%]
        tracking-[-0.005em]
        max-w-[720px]
      "
    >
      You don't have to let a legal conflict consume your life or your
      business. Let our experienced team take the burden off your shoulders.
      Contact our office today to schedule a confidential consultation and
      take the first step toward a resolution.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

